        <p>Prefer explicit version tags (e.g., <code>mostrop2p/mostro:v0.16.3</code>) over <code>:latest</code> for controlled updates.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Option B -->
      <h3 id="option-b">Option B: Docker Build (Build image locally)</h3>

      <h4>Step 5: Download Mostro</h4>
      <pre><code>cd /opt
git clone https://github.com/MostroP2P/mostro.git
